 You don't need to "believe" in Evolution, you just need to understand it. Evolution is really the only of explaining the diversity of life, right now.  />   /> If the theory of evolution were to be proved false by a better theory (Just as Einstein's theory of Gravity replaced Newtons). Biologists would be more than happy to disregard it, in favor of the better theory.  />   /> Http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evolution